com.hcl.voltmx.commons.annotations

Annotation Type VoltmxContext


  • @Target(value=PARAMETER)
 @Retention(value=RUNTIME)
public @interface VoltmxContext
    Use this annotation to mark a parameter of an exception handler (annotated with OnException) as a context parameter. Refer documentation of OnException for more details.
    See Also:
    OnException, VoltmxException
